figure.artwork:
QoS-Resources ::= < AVP Header: XXX >
                1*{ Filter-Rule }
                * [ AVP ]

IP-Address-Mask ::= < AVP Header: XXX >
                    { IP-Address }
                    { IP-Bit-Mask-Width }
                  * [ AVP ]

MAC-Address-Mask ::= < AVP Header: XXX >
                     { MAC-Address }
                     { MAC-Address-Mask-Pattern }
                   * [ AVP ]

EUI64-Address-Mask ::= < AVP Header: XXX >
                       { EUI64-Address }
                       { EUI64-Address-Mask-Pattern }
                     * [ AVP ]

section.t:
For example, a time window for 9am to 5pm (local time) from Monday to Friday would
                  be expressed as: 
                     
Time-Of-Day-Condition = {
    Time-Of-Day-Start = 32400;
    Time-Of-Day-End = 61200;
    Day-Of-Week-Mask = 
        ( MONDAY | TUESDAY | WEDNESDAY | THURSDAY | FRIDAY );
    Timezone-Flag = LOCAL;
}

